column5: Hope you had a good one but remember this, your always going to be older then me lol next years trips will give you an extra 5 min to sleep. i know old age sucks lol
Even at half the price of free.... it's still toooo much for me to do again!
Happy Happy Wayne !!!!
Happy B-day bud! Like the cake pic, too bad there's a big ugly mug ruining the picture! LMAO HH
oops .. better late than never  Happy belated !
happy bday wayne  you don't look a day over.....?  Dave
Happy B day Bud. Enjoy,as you only get one crack at that age.LOL  Cheers.
then I hope it's a good crack.....I don't get it?
Happy B day Wayne  So that makes you Fifty None years old
Wife says if I go to two... I'll be back to one, my belongings cut in half and broke PDQ !

That's just "toque head" Joe !
hey wayne   HAPPY BIRTHDAY!!!!! i have not met you yet in person..but feels like ive known you for a while...have a good one buddy...
70 is the new 60!!!  Well done brutha!!!!!!!!!!
Behave Snag... haven't made 50 yet... lol
Holy crap,  What a fast reply.  Spry young buck you are!!!   (cougars beware!, ROWWWWWWWW)

DANG... and I almost made it through the day without anyone noticing I got old... well except that PM from Bly this morning. Thanks everyone.  Been a long day... Skiied with Son and daughter #1 last night at Blue and then had to drive her back to TO around 12:30... home ~ 2:30am and up to take a vehicle into Ford for 7. Long day in the shop... and my wife that shouldn't be doin these things right now made me a neat little cake! You can see that Temagami sunburn is still peeling off my face....
Happy Birthday ya old bugger  Cool looking cake.  Hope you had a great one Wayne.  Skiing is good, cake is better  Joey
Happy Birthday Wayne - hope that through your busy schedule, you had time to enjoy it!   Don
Happy belated birthday Wayne!!
Happy Birthday Wayne.
Hope you had a great day
same here, hope you had a good day!
I donno about this.....  Leigha is far too kind to you! ha ha ha   Hope you had a great day Bud.
Happy B-Day young feller, and nice to hear it was a goodun.

Happy Birthday Wayne. I am peeling from the Florida burn!

Happy belated birthday Wayne

Happy Birthday Wayne!!!

All the best bud! Ya old fart....
Thanks everyone!  And to the Dan's... O - you're only 10 months away from catching up ! And C - I told you.. NEVER Marathon again ! lol
Happy Birthday Wayne
